Rating: 3
We liked these a lot. They were certainly easy and fast enough to make, and we thought they tasted great. Only problem: They stuck to the pan which made turning them difficult. I didn't oil the pan because I thought the potato coating would suffice, but for me it didn't. Future readers: did you have this problem and if not, what did you do to prevent sticking?

