I agree with the "easy and yummy"! I'm not sure I like it with glazed salmon, though. I'd prefer it with some kind of Mexican meat dish. Also, I had to roast the potatoes for somewhat more than 15 mins. Finally, I've learned to always replace mayo with sour cream in recipes like this, and was glad I did so.

